locality: Cap Sainte Marie, around lighthouse on headland. Exposed limestone headland, very windswept, with a covering of prostrate or mound-forming short shrubs, with open gravelly areas. Infrequent.
Bush a l'Est d'Amboasary entre Amboasary et Ranomainty.
Province: Tulear. 1 km à l'est du dèbut de la piste d'Itampolo à Ejeda.
